=============================
Integrating B-Spline Products                                          [TOC]
=============================

Computes integrals of the form

  *--[LATEX]----------------------------------------------------------------*
  |                                                                         |
  |  \int\limits_{\mathbb{R}}                                               |
  |       \varphi_1^{(\nu_1)} \left(2^{j_1} x - k_1 \right)                 |
  |       \varphi_2^{(\nu_2)} \left(2^{j_2} x - k_2 \right)                 |
  |       \;\text{d}x                                                       |
  |                                                                         |
  *-------------------------------------------------------------------------*


Code Example
============
:import: examples/integral_easy.cc [downloadable, stripped]

Compile and Run
===============

  *--[SHELL]----------------------------------------------------------------*
  |                                                                         |
  | cd examples                                                             |
  | rm -f *.o                                                               |
  | clang++ -std=c++0x -I.. -I../../FLENS/ -c ../lawa/*.cc               +++|
  |                                           ../lawa/math/*.cc             |
  | clang++ -std=c++0x -I.. -I../../FLENS/ *.o -o integral_easy          +++|
  |                                            integral_easy.cc             |
  | ./integral_easy                                                         |
  |                                                                         |
  *-------------------------------------------------------------------------*


